title: Deploy Notification Workflow
summary: Sends alerts after a deploy completes

section: Setup
step: Check deploy status | tool: deploy-api | output: status | id: check
gate: Approve release | approver: team-lead | timeout: 24h | id: approve

section: Notify
decision: Route by status | if: status == success | then: notify-ok | else: notify-fail
step: Send success notification | tool: slack | input: Deploy succeeded | depends: approve | id: notify-ok
step: Send failure alert | tool: pagerduty | input: Deploy failed | depends: check | id: notify-fail

section: Wrap-up
result: Deployment complete | depends: notify-ok
